Hello there and welcome! Thank you for taking the time out to scroll through my profile!

My name is Iziah and I am pleased to share the same wonderful experiences with my vehicles to you. I have a distinct background in helping and fulfilling other's needs.

I am getting married soon in 2022 and I really needed help with being able to give my Fianc√© the wedding she always dreamed of. I needed more income, but it had to be "passive" income as I have a full-time job and have a one year old at home with me. 

In the beginning of the year of 2021, I tried to get my Grandmother a rental car to go out of town. Every rental car company was sold out within a 100 mile radius and I did not understand why or how. I did a little research and seen that most rental car companies took a big hit during the pandemic and had to file for bankruptcy or sell their fleet...DING (Lightbulb inside my head turned on). I did more research to see how the world was handling the situation and what were the alternatives.

On YouTube, I came across somebody in Atlanta who had videos on his experiences and earnings on Turo and how this was the Airbnb on wheels. I thought this was the perfect idea for passive income to help pay for my wedding. To make sure I was making a wise decision, I used my personal car to see how it goes.

Fast forward, I now have a small fleet of 8 cars and business is booming. Not only, am I able to make extra payments for the wedding, but also able to endure and invest in more projects. What has made me successful, is to provide excellent customer service being a service provider.

Thank you for taking the time out to read my Bio and learning a little bit more about me and my services. I hope to meet you soon, safe travels!
